body:
(I was so grateful that my &#039;glitzy red carpet league event (+Draven) Got mentioned in the Skin Story Slam conclusion :D . For those interested, here is the story. Enjoy)


Upon a large magnificent red carpet, leading towards a great domed architectural wonder, a line of yordles stand upon its length, trumpets in hand and ready for the announcement. With a resounding blare from each, echoing out into the horizon, the official annual league gala has begun!

Hair as suave as ever, and a grin to match, the famous and dashing champion of Primetime, Draven was on the scene, microphone in hand.

Draven: &ldquo;Welcome Welcome, Ladies, Gentlemen, Yordles, Voidlings&hellip;Undead&hellip;er..Unspecified! Welcome to the League Gala event! Im your host, Draven, but you already knew that! Ha ha!&rdquo;

Draven looks around from his seat, taking in the crowd, as if waiting for some reaction. A disappointed look on his face, he peers around in distaste.

Draven: &ldquo;All manners of nobles, dignitaries, socialists, stars and of course, best of all, me, will be making their way to this grand event&rdquo;

Echoing from the speakers, a tiny squeaky voice is heard 

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Mr. Draven! Mr. Draven! Don&rsquo;t forget about us!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Hm? Oh yeah..&rdquo;

With what little care he could muster, Draven announces his co-hosts.

Draven: &ldquo;And at the scene, trying their best not to get stepped on, we have our reporters, the yordles Smiggles and Big Jib&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Yep! Yep!&rdquo;

Big Jib: &ldquo;Hm? Wha&rsquo;? Who said ma name?&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles plaintively: &ldquo;Wake up Jib&hellip;we&rsquo;re on&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Get that camera up and on for the arrivals Jib&hellip;and be sure to get my good side!&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Oi! Don&rsquo;t forget about me!&rdquo;

Draven rolls his eyes, exhausted with the distractions

Draven: &ldquo;And standing on the carpet is Waffles..or something&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Waffla!!&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Oh! Oh! I think the first stars are coming&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;I was already here Smiggles&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Oooooo, how amazing! Landing in a heroic stance, it&rsquo;s Galio, looking as debonair as ever!

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;I heard he got a whole new makeover&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;You bet! He&rsquo;s gliding down the carpet, a spectacle to see!&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Ooo, girls try to control yourselves, because the gentleman have just entered the party!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Well I do have a way with class&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Right&hellip;well, here come the gentlemen Cho&rsquo;gath and Gnar, looking as sophisticated as ever. Oh gosh! Gnar just kissed my hand!&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Try not to faint Waffla! We need you to stay awake&rdquo;

Big Jib: &ldquo;Did someone say cake?&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles, sighing: &ldquo;No Big Jib&hellip;, just keep the camera steady&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Oooh, Jib, Cho&rsquo;gath seems to have noticed you. What an honor!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Ha! Get ready to run fast with those legs Jibbo!&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Don&rsquo;t worry Big Jib! Officer Caitlin and the Riot squad are making sure everything goes peacefully&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Do I see glitter? It&rsquo;s seems to be flowing on the wind&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;I bet you do. I can&rsquo;t believe it. WOW! Popstar Ahri just stepped on the carpet in a shower of beautiful sparkles. Im such a fan!&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;I think I see something else going on there&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Right behind her, the amazing and dashing Taric is on the scene, wearing his shocking pink armor of the fifth age. They&rsquo;re walking down the carpet in a display of sparkles and shines. Oh oh, I wonder if they&rsquo;re dating?!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Ha!&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;He&rsquo;s definitely playing the support role well!&rdquo;

Big Jib: &ldquo;I can&rsquo;t see! I can&rsquo;t see!&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Don&rsquo;t look directly at the sparks Jib!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Who needs sparks when you got a mug like this, aye ladies?&rdquo;

Big Jib: &ldquo;Hot chocolate mug?&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Jib&hellip;I swear&hellip;.I..&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Superfan Gragas is really brewing up a storm of applause with the crowd! What a guy. Ooooo, wow!&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;What&rsquo;s going on Waffla?&rdquo;

Big Jib: &ldquo;Why does it feel so cold&hellip;&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;I&rsquo;ll tell you why! The infamous Pentakill band has just appeared. The cheers from the crowd is near deafening&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Meh..&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Lead by Mordekaiser, they&rsquo;re making their way down the carpet. OH, Sona just released a painful cord, sending their fans into a frenzy of delight!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Sending my ears right to the infirmary you mean&hellip;&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Hmm&hellip;&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;Something the matter?&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Something feels..definitely amiss here. Two large nosed and eye-glass wearing individuals have just entered. They look familiar but&hellip;im not sure. They seem to be getting strange looks.&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;Very odd. Yes, I see them now, coming down the carpet. They seem rather shifty..&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;Officer Caitlin seems to be questioning the large yellow one, I&rsquo;m not sure where this&hellip;&rdquo;

Big Jib: &ldquo;DUCK!&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles and Big Jib barely avoid a plasma ball of void energy, a misfire by one of the mysterious figures.
Waffla: &ldquo;Eeee! They seem to be causing some ruckus. People are running away while champions leap to the ready!&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;It&rsquo;s getting pretty crazy here!! Draven has leapt to the scene, axe in hand and&hellip;wow! He knocked the nose right off one of them. It&rsquo;s Vel&rsquo;koz!!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Ha ha!&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;Seems Vel&rsquo;koz was trying to go for Zilean. Officer Caitlin and the Riot squad are trying to subdue him but he is unleashing an array of shots&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;Poppy has stepped into the scene. Wow! One hit of that giant hammer and she sent Vel&rsquo;koz flying right out of the courtyard! What a yordle! What a hero!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;I did most of the work&hellip;&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;I see tentacles zooming out into the distance. He is looong gone&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;It seems the yellow one tried to sneak into the dome during the commotion. Oh&hellip;oh gosh. Is that Blitzcrank? It&rsquo;s definitely not Blitzcrank&hellip; is it?

Draven: &ldquo;What other big yellow robot do you know?&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;Yep, Officer Caitlin has caught him in her net. Seems he was banned from coming to these events after inappropriately grabbing others. Poor Blitzcrank&rdquo;

Mr.Smiggles: &ldquo;Things seem to be calming down now&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;It wouldn&rsquo;t be a League event without some action!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;And with that, let&rsquo;s take a look at our eyes in the sky. Here on Forecast duty, Janna! Let us know how it is going.&rdquo;

Janna: &ldquo;Mic check, am I coming in?&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Yeah yeah&rdquo;

Janna: &ldquo;Wait, are we rolling?&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;&hellip;Yeah&rdquo;

Janna: &ldquo;This is Janna live from the League Gala event and things are really heating up here!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;Well no sh&hellip;&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Ahem! Anything else to see, Janna?&rdquo;

Janna: &ldquo;We&rsquo;re seeing a distinct chance of Pentakills!&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;Yep they already arrived&rdquo;

Ms. Smiggles: &ldquo;How&rsquo;s the weather looking?&rdquo;

Janna: &ldquo;iiit&rsquo;s gusty!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;The wind&rsquo;s as dead as the Shurima dessert&hellip;what are you&hellip;&rdquo;

A large gust of wind comes flying in from above.

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Oooh, looks like Draven just got blown right off his chair. Thank you Janna for the update and surprise gale force. How&rsquo;s it looking at the front, Waffla?&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;The oh so debonair Ezreal has made an appearance and the girls have gone wild. Oh, appearing by his side is the beautiful and stunning Lux, wearing a gown of shifting elemental colors. How amazing!&rdquo;

Waffla: &ldquo;As the last of the nobles and stars make their way inside, it looks like it is quieting down here, back to you Mr. Smiggles.&rdquo;

Mr. Smiggles: &ldquo;Thanks Waffla, it was quite a spectacle to be sure! They seem to be starting up inside, let&rsquo;s go enjoy the show!&rdquo;

Draven: &ldquo;This is Draven, signing out. Autographed pictures of yours truly handed out for 30 mins after the show. Get them while you can!&rdquo;
